<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA73">
<l>pūvaiyuṅ kāyāvu nīlamum pūkkiṉṟa</l>
<l>kāvi malareṉṟuṅ kāṇṭōṟu pāviyēṉ</l>
<l>mellāvi meymikavē pūrikku mavvavai</l>
<l>yellām pirāṉuruvē yeṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bilberry, ironwood, blue lotus, flowering</l>
<l>water-lilies – whenever I see such blossoms the soft soul</l>
<l>[and] body of me evil-doer are very full, thinking that all those</l>
<l>are the forms of the lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
